---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="Weathering, Mass Wasting & Erosion" description="Weathering, mass wasting, and erosion processes in Peru.">

  <section class="bg-gradient-to-br from-orange-600 to-amber-900 text-white py-16 px-4">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
      <p class="text-orange-200 uppercase tracking-widest text-sm mb-2">Earth Processes · Week 3</p>
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-3">Weathering, Mass Wasting & Erosion</h1>
      <p class="text-orange-100 text-lg">How rain, ice, gravity, and time sculpt Peru's dramatic landscapes.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-16">
    <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl border border-dashed border-orange-300 p-12 text-center shadow-sm">
      <div class="text-5xl mb-4"></div>
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-stone-700 mb-2">Content Coming Soon</h2>
      <p class="text-stone-500 mb-6 max-w-md mx-auto">
        This page will explore how chemical and physical weathering, landslides (huaycos), and erosion shape Peru's terrain from the Andes to the coast.
      </p>
      <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-3 gap-4 text-left max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        {[
          { icon: "", title: "Chemical & Physical Weathering", desc: "Freeze-thaw cycles and acid weathering in the Andes" },
          { icon: "", title: "Huaycos & Landslides", desc: "Peru's deadly mass wasting events and their causes" },
          { icon: "", title: "Erosion Patterns", desc: "Wind and water erosion in coastal deserts and river valleys" },
        ].map(item => (
          <div class="bg-orange-50 rounded-xl p-4">
            <div class="text-2xl mb-1">{item.icon}</div>
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-stone-700 text-sm mb-1">{item.title}</h3>
            <p class="text-stone-500 text-xs">{item.desc}</p>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
